snippet.title: Darksburg - PVP Trailer
snippet.description:
In Darksburg, you can choose to play against the AI or face a much greater challenge!
Will you choose to play as the Survivors? Or as the Revenants?

You can already wishlist Darksburg on Steam: https://bit.ly/2WWYAbq

Learn more about the game: http://darksburg.com
